00:02:59.460 --> 00:03:01.990 align:middle line:84%
enormous belief
systems that again

00:03:01.990 --> 00:03:06.360 align:middle line:84%
have got traction, but
people don't really

00:03:06.360 --> 00:03:09.714 align:middle line:84%
