They're seeded for their
abilities to do that.

00:37:25.784 --> 00:37:27.950 align:middle line:84%
But again, it's the same
thing you're talking about,

00:37:27.950 --> 00:37:31.350 align:middle line:84%
this 140,000 some that are
here to seed us downward.

00:37:31.350 --> 00:37:34.180 align:middle line:84%
He'd say, no, they're
here to seed us upward.

00:37:34.180 --> 00:37:35.330 align:middle line:90%
What's your take on that?

00:37:35.330 --> 00:37:38.050 align:middle line:84%
>>KRAMER: So soul
classifications,

00:37:38.050 --> 00:37:41.920 align:middle line:84%
there's a kind of
human who has a soul,

00:37:41.920 --> 00:37:45.560 align:middle line:84%
an independent soul that's
had thousands of lives

00:37:45.560 --> 00:37:48.680 align:middle line:84%
and has built this
incredible vessel which

00:37:48.680 --> 00:37:51.720 align:middle line:84%
is like a chronicle
of incredible learning

00:37:51.720 --> 00:37:53.170 align:middle line:90%
through many worlds.

00:37:53.170 --> 00:37:59.250 align:middle line:84%
And that is an ensouled human,
E-N-S-O-U-L-E-D, ensouled,

00:37:59.250 --> 00:38:01.230 align:middle line:90%
i.e., has a soul.

00:38:01.230 --> 00:38:03.440 align:middle line:84%
There are group-soul
humans, right,

00:38:03.440 --> 00:38:06.140 align:middle line:84%
where there's no need
for an individual soul,

00:38:06.140 --> 00:38:07.770 align:middle line:84%
because they're
not doing anything.

00:38:07.770 --> 00:38:10.270 align:middle line:84%
They're just living,
breathing, going to work,

00:38:10.270 --> 00:38:12.910 align:middle line:84%
having families,
smiling, falling in love,

00:38:12.910 --> 00:38:13.710 align:middle line:90%
cooking dinner.

00:38:13.710 --> 00:38:16.350 align:middle line:84%
Nothing wrong with that, but
no need for an individual soul.

00:38:16.350 --> 00:38:18.000 align:middle line:90%
They've not built it yet.

00:38:18.000 --> 00:38:21.750 align:middle line:84%
So the soul isn't necessarily
as you might say God-given.

00:38:21.750 --> 00:38:25.490 align:middle line:84%
It's built, built by the
individual, by their own will.

00:38:25.490 --> 00:38:27.840 align:middle line:84%
When that hasn't taken
place, there's a group soul,

00:38:27.840 --> 00:38:31.170 align:middle line:84%
so many kind of
anthroposophists who

00:38:31.170 --> 00:38:34.210 align:middle line:84%
were studying under
Steiner in the early 1900s

00:38:34.210 --> 00:38:36.180 align:middle line:84%
would say animals are
a classic example.

00:38:36.180 --> 00:38:38.850 align:middle line:84%
Animals-- most animals
don't need souls.

00:38:38.850 --> 00:38:41.410 align:middle line:84%
Some do, because they
do extraordinary things.

00:38:41.410 --> 00:38:44.360 align:middle line:84%
And many dog and cat owners
will think, yes, my dog's one

00:38:44.360 --> 00:38:45.720 align:middle line:90%
of those special animals.

00:38:45.720 --> 00:38:45.900 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:38:45.900 --> 00:38:46.490 align:middle line:90%
I have one.

00:38:46.490 --> 00:38:47.110 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: Yeah, see.

00:38:47.110 --> 00:38:48.070 align:middle line:90%
There you go.

00:38:48.070 --> 00:38:51.170 align:middle line:90%
So anybody can build a soul.

00:38:51.170 --> 00:38:53.160 align:middle line:90%
Any thing can build a soul.

00:38:53.160 --> 00:38:53.960 align:middle line:90%
So there's that.

00:38:53.960 --> 00:38:56.400 align:middle line:84%
So there's individual
souls, group souls,

00:38:56.400 --> 00:38:59.520 align:middle line:84%
and then un-ensouled,
which again, you

00:38:59.520 --> 00:39:02.030 align:middle line:84%
know, you think, oh, that
sounds like it is-- no problem.

00:39:02.030 --> 00:39:03.210 align:middle line:90%
No problem.

00:39:03.210 --> 00:39:05.790 align:middle line:84%
Wouldn't it be kind
of beautiful in a way

00:39:05.790 --> 00:39:08.542 align:middle line:84%
to come in and say, OK,
you've got 100 years.

00:39:08.542 --> 00:39:10.250 align:middle line:84%
You're bullet-proof,
because when you go,

00:39:10.250 --> 00:39:12.436 align:middle line:84%
you're going home to
the divine anyway,

00:39:12.436 --> 00:39:13.560 align:middle line:90%
so there's nothing to lose.

00:39:13.560 --> 00:39:14.990 align:middle line:84%
But you don't need
to do anything.

00:39:14.990 --> 00:39:17.900 align:middle line:84%
You just come here,
have a wonderful time,

00:39:17.900 --> 00:39:22.490 align:middle line:84%
see the beauty, you know,
love people, be together,

00:39:22.490 --> 00:39:24.750 align:middle line:84%
travel the world, watch
the red sunset light,

00:39:24.750 --> 00:39:27.150 align:middle line:84%
as I did flying in over
the Rockies last night.

00:39:27.150 --> 00:39:30.690 align:middle line:84%
Just exquisite, you know,
unbelievable thing to see.

00:39:30.690 --> 00:39:33.949 align:middle line:84%
I mean, you see this all
the time, but unbelievable.

00:39:33.949 --> 00:39:35.490 align:middle line:84%
And then when you're
dead, that's it.

00:39:35.490 --> 00:39:36.500 align:middle line:90%
You're done.

00:39:36.500 --> 00:39:38.220 align:middle line:90%
And then maybe that's all.

00:39:38.220 --> 00:39:39.320 align:middle line:90%
Who cares, right?

00:39:39.320 --> 00:39:41.880 align:middle line:84%
So there's these
different classifications.

00:39:41.880 --> 00:39:45.570 align:middle line:84%
Only the individual souls
have the responsibility,

00:39:45.570 --> 00:39:48.650 align:middle line:90%
self-chosen, to make this.

00:39:48.650 --> 00:39:51.210 align:middle line:84%
And the only thing they
have to be careful of

00:39:51.210 --> 00:39:54.100 align:middle line:84%
is that they can be
deceived to make something

00:39:54.100 --> 00:39:55.430 align:middle line:90%
that they wouldn't wish to.

00:39:55.430 --> 00:39:56.230 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:39:56.230 --> 00:39:57.320 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: And that's the trick.

00:39:57.320 --> 00:39:58.620 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And too
easily, sometimes.

