or whatever, or to
think that the men who

00:46:10.530 --> 00:46:13.810 align:middle line:84%
were doing the quote,
"standoff" in Oregon

00:46:13.810 --> 00:46:17.510 align:middle line:84%
are stupid preppers or
brave Constitutionalists.

00:46:17.510 --> 00:46:18.310 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:46:18.310 --> 00:46:19.934 align:middle line:84%
>>KRAMER: It's one
or the other, right?

00:46:19.934 --> 00:46:23.030 align:middle line:84%
It's one or the other and
there's no middle ground.

00:46:23.030 --> 00:46:24.600 align:middle line:90%
That doesn't exist.

