00:59:35.010 --> 00:59:38.250 align:middle line:10%
with the political
process in the States,

00:59:38.250 --> 00:59:41.960 align:middle line:10%
which is very fascinating
and worth a look,

00:59:41.960 --> 00:59:47.560 align:middle line:10%
it's a lovely opportunity to
check our own polarizations

00:59:47.560 --> 00:59:50.530 align:middle line:10%
and our instincts to polarize,
sometimes say this is wrong

00:59:50.530 --> 00:59:52.690 align:middle line:10%
and this is right.

00:59:52.690 --> 00:59:54.766 align:middle line:84%
You can only really
do that for yourself.

00:59:54.766 --> 00:59:56.510 align:middle line:84%
You can't have the
screen tell you that.

00:59:56.510 --> 01:00:00.270 align:middle line:84%
You can't have--
you know, I can't

01:00:00.270 --> 01:00:05.075 align:middle line:84%
remember these people's names,
Rachel Maddow or Bill O'Reilly

01:00:05.075 --> 01:00:10.035 align:middle line:84%
or Megyn Kelly or all these
crazy left and righters.

01:00:10.035 --> 01:00:11.160 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: All the analysts.

01:00:11.160 --> 01:00:13.530 align:middle line:84%
>>KRAMER: You can't have
those people tell you

01:00:13.530 --> 01:00:14.450 align:middle line:90%
the way to do things.

01:00:14.450 --> 01:00:19.560 align:middle line:84%
The only way to do it really is
switch that stuff off, go out,

01:00:19.560 --> 01:00:22.720 align:middle line:84%
talk to people, breathe,
watch the sunset,

01:00:22.720 --> 01:00:24.560 align:middle line:84%
make some determinations
for yourself.

01:00:24.560 --> 01:00:25.360 align:middle line:90%
Look at your life.

01:00:25.360 --> 01:00:26.370 align:middle line:90%
Look at your family.

01:00:26.370 --> 01:00:27.560 align:middle line:90%
Look at what you're doing.

01:00:27.560 --> 01:00:30.400 align:middle line:84%
Look-- are you serious about
your own transformation,

01:00:30.400 --> 01:00:32.970 align:middle line:84%
or do you just want to
rearrange the furniture?

01:00:32.970 --> 01:00:38.710 align:middle line:84%
And in that process of
consistent re-evaluation

01:00:38.710 --> 01:00:40.690 align:middle line:84%
of one's self, you
come to the point

01:00:40.690 --> 01:00:44.230 align:middle line:84%
where you cease to buy
into that polarization

01:00:44.230 --> 01:00:46.590 align:middle line:84%
and you start to
collapse it and move on

01:00:46.590 --> 01:00:48.520 align:middle line:84%
and transcend that
whole paradigm.

01:00:48.520 --> 01:00:50.780 align:middle line:90%
And then you're creating this.

01:00:50.780 --> 01:00:53.230 align:middle line:84%
You're not creating what
someone else has dictated.

01:00:53.230 --> 01:00:54.420 align:middle line:90%
You're doing it yourself.

01:00:54.420 --> 01:00:55.800 align:middle line:90%
And that changes the world.

01:00:55.800 --> 01:00:58.170 align:middle line:90%
That brings the Earth changes.

01:00:58.170 --> 01:00:59.380 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

